<plot>This Original six-part television series, created for Bravo! is a unique aboriginal dance series featuring an eloquent union of First Nation storytelling, beautiful, haunting, stylized, hip-hop, traditional drum &amp; singing music, modern &amp; traditional dance styles interpreting age old stories connecting to the rite of passage of the soul and creation. These six different dance pieces were created and filmed in the locations of their origin. The bands include: Inuit, Ojibwa, Cree and Iroquois.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?125745</url></doc>
